Appendix: GM Notes & Scaling
Adjusting for Party Size
For 5 Players: Add 1x Blackwater Sentry to Section 1 and 1x Blackwater Deckhand to Section 4.
For 2 Players: Remove the Lookout in Section 1 and reduce Captain ValenΓÇÖs HP to 30.
Dynamic Difficulty Adjustment
If the Party Struggles:
Section 2: The "Hidden Sentry" (Mage) is asleep and does not wake up unless attacked directly or the bridge slams down violently.
Section 3: The Bear is Sickly (reduce HP to 15) or the trap mechanism is rusted and fails to open on the first trigger.
Section 4: Captain Valen forgets to use his Amulet reaction on the first hit, arrogant in his skill.
If the Party Dominates:
