Roleplaying Orthus Endario
Voice: High-pitched, fast, nervous.
Behavior: He constantly wipes his forehead with a handkerchief. He is terrified of "The Company" more than death itself.
Relationship: He is a coward, but he pays well. If the players treat him with respect, he becomes a useful (if jittery) contact for smuggling goods into Solitude later.

