Tactical Intel (Read Before Building)
This mission takes place in a Sea Cave. Adjust your build accordingly:
Don't Sink: There is deep, cold water. Heavy Armor is risky if you fall in. Athletics (Might) will be useful for swimming and climbing.
Verticality: There are watchtowers, rigging, and cliffs. Ranged options (Archery/Magic) are highly recommended for at least one party member.
The Environment: You are fighting intelligent pirates, not mindless zombies. Stealth (Agility) or Deception (Guile) might let you get the drop on them before the alarm is raised.
